# PSANP Abstractions

![Build status](https://gitlab.geo-sat.com/rnd/production/libs/psanp-abstractions/badges/master/pipeline.svg)
![Coverage report](https://gitlab.geo-sat.com/rnd/production/libs/psanp-abstractions/badges/master/coverage.svg)
![Latest Release](https://gitlab.geo-sat.com/rnd/production/libs/psanp-abstractions/-/badges/release.svg)

*psanp-abstractions* is a project that contains all the tools needed to implement a *psanp* `Classifier`.

# Documentation

The documentation is available [here](http://geosat-docs.s3-website.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/psanp-abstractions/master/index.html)
